<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hanneman Echter von Mespelbrunn, Viztum von Aschaffenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Unterstützung wegen des Überfalls auf Nürnberger Kaufleute.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_272" id="135v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_272_r1l33"><expan>Ha<ex>n</ex>man</expan> <expan>Echt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Vicʒt<ex>um</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>Oſchaffe<ex>n</ex>b<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_272_r1l34">Lieber her vicʒtüm / . Als die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒü ew kumen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> der nam </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l35">wegen als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>kawflewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l36">Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ewr hilffe vnd fürdrung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l37">dar cʒü tun wöllet / daʒ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> daʒ Jr <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gekeret <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l38">vnd ſie <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>günſtıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beuolhen ſein <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_272_r1l39">Als etc vnd das etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_272" id="135v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ha<ex>n</ex>man</expan>
<expan>Echt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>viczt<ex>um</ex></expan> czü
                                <expan>Oschaffe<ex>n</ex>b<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her vicztüm, als die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czü ew kumen
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> der nam wegen, als
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>kawflewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ewr hilffe und fürdrung dar czü tun
                        wöllet, daz den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> daz ir
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gekeret <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und sie
                                <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>günstiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bevolhen sein
                            <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet. Als etc. Und das etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
